Brambickle is a gnomish explorer located atop the Trollweiss Mountain. He may ask for a hard order in the Gnome Restaurant minigame. To get to Brambickle you do not need to have completed Troll Romance. Many players find it tedious to deliver to him, so most usually refuse to take the order, and wait five minutes for another one.

To find Brambickle, teleport to Trollheim and head towards the north-west path towards the Ice Path and Ice Gate. Be careful not to head west towards Troll Stronghold or north to the thrower trolls and God Wars Dungeon. Upon reaching the Ice Gate, head north-west through the snow and enter the cave. DO NOT GO THROUGH THE ICE GATE. Turn on Protect from Melee to avoid damage from the Ice trolls or bring food if you cannot and are low level. Follow the cave north and exit through the crevasse in the most north-western area on the northern wall. Brambickle is on the plateau just south of the cave exit.

Treasure Trails[edit | edit source]

Brambickle is the solution to the hard anagram clue: BAKER CLIMB.
